    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Community places for the regular assembly or congregation of Jews for liturgical services, assembly, and study apart from the service of the temple; since the destruction of the temple in Jerusalem, worship at the synagogue is the sole place of public worship.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
